Join the CRSSJ’s Rabbi Sarah, Imam Abdul Muhaymin, and Rev. Cassandra for lunch, conversation, and reflection on how to navigate personal identities and communities. We will discuss how to stay true to our own identities and values, while being open to others and leaving room for change.


Lunch will be provided.&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;


Students, Faculty and Staff welcome to attend.

